			<div class="bookname">
				<h1>第十八卷:第一章 彼岸之桥</h1>
				<div class="bottem1">
					<a href="/book/zhongshengzhiemolieren/5082759.shtml">上一章</a> ← <a href="/book/zhongshengzhiemolieren/">章节列表</a> → <a href="/book/zhongshengzhiemolieren/5083052.shtml">下一章</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="javascript:;" onclick="addBookMark(5082760,2567);">加入书签</a>
				</div>
				<div class="lm">推荐阅读：<a href="/book/mengmoshijiezhiqihuan/">梦魔世界之奇幻</a><a href="/book/junduixitong/">军队系统</a><a href="/book/liemengxingzhe/">猎梦行者</a><a href="/book/heikexiaoyaoyou/">黑客逍遥游</a><a href="/book/doushizhenfashi/">都市阵法师</a><a href="/book/gaodazhuangdelanqiuqiji/">高大壮的篮球奇迹</a><a href="/book/sanguozhibangdiedangjunfa/">三国之帮爹当军阀</a><a href="/book/zouyinren/">走阴人</a><a href="/book/zhongshengzhijiandangbahuang/">重生之剑荡八荒</a><a href="/book/guiyuantianju/">闺园甜居</a></div>
